article_title: Park caretaker for Town of Windsor shot and killed while bicycling – The Denver Post
article_text: Climbers on Friday found the body of one of two Indians who went missing near the top of Mount Everest, while a helicopter brought back the body of an Australian woman who died on the mountain. Worsening weather was forcing everyone to descend to safety, with the last missing climber presumed dead.
